title: PacketTracer61_Build87_setup.exe
description:
NOte: It has a beta timer. I dont know the time but it could be anytime from September 2013(first mentioned) up to January 2014(upload date I found).

The timer is in the PT executable after installation.

For MAC OS X this program can be WineWrapper to start your CCNA studies but netacad.com still will not support Mac OS for exam portions.

As always nothing beats the real thing as wiring up your CCNA lab equipment and hearing it hum along.
